{"tha-ap515:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap515:0.2":"Phaladayakavagga ","tha-ap515:0.3":"3 Kosambaphaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap515:1.1":"“Kakudham vilasantamva, ","tha-ap515:1.2":"devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap515:1.3":"Rathiyam patipajjantam, ","tha-ap515:1.4":"kosambam adadim tada. ","tha-ap515:2.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap515:2.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap515:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap515:2.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap515:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap515:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap515:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap515:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap515:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap515:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap515:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap515:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap515:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap515:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kosambaphaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap515:7.1":"Kosambaphaliyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}